Gloucester Street Learning Centre

Gloucester Street Community Centre is a registered educational HUB offering a variety of courses throughout the year including: 
Employment into Early Years and Health Care; 
Functional Skills English and Maths; 
Beginners IT; 
Paediatric First Aid; 
Employability Skills ; 
Food Safety and Catering; 
Manual Handling; 
Employment into Cleaning.

Please note: There is a cost incurred for anyone who is unable to provide proof of their unemployment status and right to live and work in the UK.
